Text: By the way, Dr. Shalom, it's hoes down, g's up not the other way around you Borat emulating mofo!!

My dear Filthypino friend, you have excellent taste in music as well as excellent taste in friends.  I have read your memoirs and I wanted you to know that Rabbi Gordon has also been an inspiration to me and I hope to demonstrate the "Busting a Gordon" technique to you when I see you in March.  May PikeyShalom be in your heart always!
